gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Trail Blazers 130, 76ers 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Blazers defeated the 76ers, 130-104. Jerami Grant (27 points, five rebounds, three assists), Malcolm Brogdon (24 points, five rebounds, nine assists), and Scoot Henderson (22 points, three 3PT, four assists) totaled 73 points for Portland in the win. Kelly Oubre Jr. (25 points, six rebounds) led Philadelphia in defeat. The Blazers improve to 14-33 as the 76ers move to 29-16.
